using Distributions, CairoMakie

N = Normal(0, 1)

Pf = range(10^-4, 10^-1, 301)
Pd = range(0.2, 0.9, 201)
d = @. (quantile(N, 1 - Pd') - quantile(N, 1 - Pf))^2
d_decibels = 10log10.(d)

contour(Pf, Pd, d_decibels, labels = true)

using Distributions, CairoMakie

Xmin = -3
Xmax = 4
NX = 301

mu0 = 0
mu1 = 1
h = mu0 + 3/4 * (mu1 - mu0)

H0 = Normal(mu0, 1)
H1 = Normal(mu1, 1)
X = range(Xmin, Xmax, NX)
p0 = pdf.(H0, X)
p1 = pdf.(H1, X)

fig = Figure()
axis = Axis(fig[1, 1])

lines!(axis, X, p0)
lines!(axis, X, p1)

Xh = range(h, Xmax, NX)

ph0 = pdf.(H0, Xh)
ph1 = pdf.(H1, Xh)
